Bonus Features:

Saving image to a .ppm file:

Please specify the filename (along with the .ppm extension) after the "-f" option. For example, "-f 123.ppm".
Then, after you open the image, press "s" to save the file in the same directory under the specified filename.
The program will exit and you can then open the image.